<h1>Become an Editor</h1>

<h2>What does an editor do?</h2>
<p>An editor performs a few tasks. The first is to review submissions made against the directory and approve them if they
would make a good contribution. They also maintain the existing submissions ensuring the remain relevant and if not
remove them from the directory.</p>

<h2>How do I become an editor?</h2>
<p>At the moment please apply by asking to be added by using twitter @boyter or email ben@boyter.org </p>


<h2>Requirements?</h2>
<p>Beyond having a reasonably good sense of judgement and an internet connection nothing is required.</p>


